Currency Converter

This is a simple Python program that converts one currency to another using real-time exchange rates.

How to Use

Run the program.

Enter the amount you want to convert.

Enter the currency you are converting from (e.g., USD).

Enter the currency you are converting to (e.g., PKR).

The program will show the converted amount.

Requirements

Python installed

Internet connection

Install requests library using:

pip install requests

Example
Enter amount to convert: 100
From currency: USD
To currency: PKR
100 USD = 27800.50 PKR
